Package com.mygdx.pirategame.configs

Class GameSave

java.lang.Object
com.mygdx.pirategame.configs.GameSave
public class GameSave
extends java.lang.Object
GameSave The class manages the saving and loading phases of the game. To do so, it only get the important information about the main classes in the project and it serializes them (convert into bytes) and writes them onto a json file.
Author:
Davide Bressani
